#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-alpha-disk.xml:263
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"On Alpha based systems you don't need a separate boot slice. However, the\n"
"first cylinder cannot be used as the <c>aboot</c> image will be placed there.\n"
